Package com.example.musiquest

package com.example.musiquest
  • Class
    Description
    Alerts
    The Alerts class represents the activity for displaying alert options to the user in the MusiQuest application.
    GameActivity
    The activity responsible for managing the game, displaying questions, and handling user answers.
    HomePage
    The HomePage class represents the main page of the MusiQuest application where users can navigate to different features such as playing the game, viewing their profile, checking the leaderboard, and accessing alerts.
    Leaderboard
    The activity displaying the leaderboard and providing WebSocket communication.
    LoginPage
    The `LoginPage` class represents the user interface for user authentication.
    MainActivity
    The main activity of the MusiQuest application.
    Player
    The Player class represents a player in the MusiQuest application, including both current player information and leaderboard player information.
    ProfilePage
    The ProfilePage class represents the user profile page in the MusiQuest application.
    RegisterPage
    The RegisterPage class handles user registration, including capturing user details like email, username, password, account type, and avatar selection.
    WebSocketListener
    Interface defining methods for handling WebSocket events.
    WebSocketMain
    The WebSocketMain class represents the main activity for WebSocket-based chat functionality in the MusiQuest app.
    WebSocketManager
    Singleton WebSocketManager instance used for managing WebSocket connections in the Android application.
